    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 20th level, you become an avatar of peace, which gives you the following benefits.</p><ul><li><p>You have <strong>resistance</strong> to all damage dealt by other creatures (their attacks, spells, and other effects).</p></li><li><p>Whenever a creature damages you, it takes <strong>radiant damage</strong> equal to half the amount it dealt to you.</p></li></ul><p>If you attack a creature, cast a spell on it, or deal damage to it by any means but this feature, neither benefit works against that creature until you finish a <strong>long rest</strong>.</p>",
